	<h1>Program Internship Requirement</h1>
	<p>If apply, please first finish the Program Intern application form.</p>
	<p>second, also complete the Pledge of Confidentiality pdf, the Non-disclosure Form pdf and the Reference Form pdf in Resouces above and send to info@scottyshouse.org</p>

	<div>

	
	<ol>
		<li>All interns must be at least 18 years of age.</li>
		<li>Interns must successfully pass a CPS and criminal background check.</li>
		<li>All interns must successfully complete an initial orientation provided by Scotty's House. </li>
		<li>Interns must maintain absolute confidentiality at all times.  A confidentiality agreement must be signed by the intern prior to the initial interview.</li>
		<li>Interns must be willing to work within the guidelines, policies and standards of Scotty's House.</li>
		<li>Interns must demonstrate sensitivity to cultural and ethnic differences.</li>
		<li>Interns must demonstrate willingness to work as part of a team on behalf of the children served by Scotty's House.</li>
		<li>Interns must submit a completed application packet (including three references) before he/she will be contacted for an interview.</li>
		<li>Interns must submit work schedule during the initial interview.</li>
		
	</ol>

	
	
